HEADWORD: Irrefrangible
<hw>Ir`re*fran"gi*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not
refrangible; that can not be refracted in passing from one medium to
another.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Ir`re*fran"gi*ble*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Irrefutable</ent>⟦br⟧
